---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Clienvora"
	description="Strategic B2B growth and conversion engineering."
	pubDate={new Date('June 18 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
		At Clienvora, we believe that B2B growth is not about guessing; it is about engineering. 
		We specialize in building organic conversion frameworks that turn complex enterprise 
		offerings into clear, high-impact narratives that decision makers actually understand.
	</p>

	<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
		In an era of noisy marketing, we focus on the architecture behind the content. By aligning 
		Technical SEO with high-intent conversion copywriting, we ensure your critical assets 
		are not just seen, but indexed and valued by the right audience.
	</p>

	<h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mt-12 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h3>
	<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
		We move away from vanity metrics. Our goal is to map your business features cleanly into 
		the mental models of your enterprise prospects. We believe that good design serves 
		strategy, and that technical precision is the backbone of sustainable pipeline growth.
	</p>

	<h3 class="text-2xl font-medium mt-12 mb-4">Let's Connect</h3>
	<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
		If you are looking to refine your B2B strategy, improve your technical SEO, or transform 
		your conversion copy, let’s talk. You can reach out directly via 
		<a href="https://wa.me/923204779972" target="_blank" class="font-bold border-b border-black hover:opacity-70 transition">WhatsApp</a> 
		or view our 
		<a href="https://www.clienvora.com" target="_blank" class="font-bold border-b border-black hover:opacity-70 transition">official website</a> 
		to learn more.
	</p>
</Layout>
